Color

- color-name
- hexa-code
- rgb()
  Number System
- binary -> base 2 (0 - 1)
- octal -> base 8 (0 - 7)
- decimal -> base 10 (0 - 9)
- hexadecimal -> base 16 (0 - 9) (a - f) -> (0 - f)
  Hexa-code -> rgb => #rrggbb ->
  #ff0000 => #f00
  #00ff00 => #0f0
  #0000ff => #00f
  #000000 => #000
  #ffffff => #fff
