Font properties

- font-family
- font-size
- font-style
- font-weight
- line-height
  font-family/ font group (computer system)
  -serif => stroke => Times New Roman
  -sans-serif => non-stroke => Arial
  -monospace => one+space => fixed -width => Courier
  -cursive => handwriting => Lucida Handwriting
  -fantasy => Jokerman
  font-size - px (Fixed unit) - % , em (relative unit) - rem (relative unit) - fr
  font-style
  -normal, italic, oblique
  font-weight - normal, bold, bolder , 100, 200, 300, ... 900
